Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.58,0:00:55.73,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}I've been ignoring everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.73,0:00:58.03,EN-op,,0,0,0,,I've been wandering around
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.03,0:01:02.43,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I've been deceived everything. At that time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.79,0:01:07.48,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Then you appeared in front of me. You ignited my pale heart
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.50,0:01:11.78,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}We've been looking for each other from now on
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.80,0:01:12.99,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Save you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.14,0:01:18.58,JP-op,,0,0,0,,際限ない犠牲を
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.06,0:01:23.96,JP-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}朦朧とした理想を
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.73,0:01:27.71,JP-op,,0,0,0,,もう無駄にしないようにと
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.71,0:01:32.33,JP-op,,0,0,0,,悲しみを切り刻んだ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.03,0:01:35.35,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.35,0:01:38.58,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Get away from dark nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.60,0:01:42.77,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Just now. Chip at your heart. We just fight for freedom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.90,0:01:47.48,JP-op,,0,0,0,,奪い合って　汚し合って
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.48,0:01:51.67,JP-op,,0,0,0,,それでも守りたくて
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.84,0:01:54.07,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.07,0:01:57.53,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from dark nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.54,0:02:02.04,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}We don't want to go through that again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.04,0:02:07.61,JP-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}時は満ちた　始まりの鐘が鳴る
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.57,0:02:14.64,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}Get away from me
